description:
My name is Nojima Yuya. I currently studying for my tests to enter a good college.

Suddenly, my mom gets me a tutor, a beautiful young college student named Nishijima Kaho. This is unexpected but good. What is bad is that I so nervous and I keep getting...

&quot;Anything wrong, Yuya?&quot; &quot;No, I... I just don't have any motivation to study!&quot;

orz ... A bad start. I wonder what she thinks of me...?
___

&quot;...I don't think that's the case.&quot;

I was worried at first, but he's a good kid. I want to be tougher, to give him better motivation, but I think I already started wrong. I have to properly...

Oh no! I split water on my shirt!
___

&quot;Are you alright?! Here, use this tissue to...&quot; Oh no. I just touched her breast, didn't I...

&quot;...I'm so sorry!&quot;

... &lt;3

&quot;Yuya-kun, if... you get a good result on your next test, I'll let you touch them as a reward.&quot;

&quot;Eh...?&quot;
_______

So begins a convoluted teacher/student relationship. Only time will tell where it may lead.
